title: Football, Back! Plus holdouts, NFC West with Brady Quinn (Football 8/2)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and Brady Quinn break down the latest news and notes from around the NFL, including Melvin Gordon's trade request (9:30), Ryan Kalil returning (20:15), Cowboys chatter (25:00), the reality of Michael Thomas' contract (32:30), Tom Brady's weight gain and contract (35:00) and some NFC West training camp battles (49:00).
